snippet.title: Even More Celebrities SPEAK OUT Against James Franco
snippet.description:
Even More Celebrities SPEAK OUT Against James Franco
Over the past many years, we’ve been hearing story after story of how certain Hollywood stars aren’t who they appear to be. Some of them just have terrible political views and choose to support people Some, however, have been accused of, and proven to be in some cases, terrible people who prey on others because their station “gives them power”. One such person is apparently James Franco, who has been accused of being a kind of by someone who worked on a certain movie with him. We’ll break it down for you.
